laden: Command and Config Fetcher
Juan Pedro Paredes Caballero <juampe@iquis.com>

Send commands to hosts or hosts group and save the output in a repository in order to audit later 
The hosts have to be accesibe by rsh (Prefered SSH flavour with key authentication) and included in /etc/hosts too

group to define groups of hosts

Use
Command modes: view cmd file
        mode view(v)
        mode cmd(c)
        mode file(f)
Append modes: append noappend
        mode append(>>):
        mode noappend(>):
Commands: host group repository select quit
        group(g):       [group]
        host(h):        [host] [host] ...
        repository(r)
        select(s)
        quit(q)

